This story is from January 15, 2020

parking at Govardhan Nagar Bus Stop

@RoadsOfMumbai @mtptraffic @MumbaiTraffics in spite of repeated reminders followed by assurances of taking necessary actions, no change in situation. Govardhan Nagar Bus Stop, Poisar Gymkhana, Kandivali West. Passengers unable to stand. area fully covered.
